de.intarsys.security.smartcard.pcsc.nativec

Class _PCSC

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.intarsys.security.smartcard.pcsc.nativec._PCSC
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    _IPCSC, _PCSC_RETURN_CODES

    public class _PCSC
extends java.lang.Object
implements _IPCSC
    The concrete intarsys native-c based PC/SC wrapper declaration. The implementation by default auto-detects the platform and selects the native library. As an alternative you can provide an explicit native library name.
